      <data key="d1">The **STREAM_DATE** entity represents the original date of a streaming event, stored as text in the standardized 'DD-Mon-YYYY' format (e.g., "01-Jan-2023"). As a textual field, it cannot be used directly for date-based calculations or temporal analysis and requires conversion into a structured date format to derive meaningful metrics. This attribute serves as the foundational source for all downstream temporal operations, ensuring consistency in event tracking while necessitating additional processing for practical use in analytics or reporting.</data>
