      <data key="d1">Based on the provided data for the entity **INVOICE_DATE**, the consolidated description is:

**INVOICE_DATE** represents the date when an invoice was issued or generated. The date is stored as a text string in the `MM/DD/YY` format. Due to its textual representation, this field requires standardization (conversion to a proper date data type) to enable date operations and support derived metrics (e.g., day/month/year extraction, date arithmetic, or temporal analytics). Both descriptions emphasize the necessity of transforming this raw text value into a standardized date format for practical use in data processing.</data>
