   Defines the billing period/coverage period for services (from Descriptions 1 and 2).  
3. **Data Format**:  
   Stores values as date range strings (e.g., "2023-01-01 to 2023-01-31") to denote start/end dates (from Description 3).  
4. **Semantic Meaning**:  
   Represents the active service duration tied to a billing document (invoice record), ensuring clarity on what timeframe the charges encompass (from Descriptions 1 and 2).  

No contradictions exist; all descriptions align to reinforce SERVICE_PERIOD's role as a temporal anchor within the invoice data model.</data>
